  "title": "chore(examples): update demos to use instantsearch from repo",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for submitting a pull request!\r\n  Please provide enough information so that others can review your pull request.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Summary**\r\n\r\nTo improve InstantSearch releases reliability we plan to add some [End-2-End tests](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch-e2e-tests) in addition to our existing unit test suite.\r\n\r\nSince we'll use the [e-commerce demo](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/tree/develop/examples/e-commerce) to run our tests then we need to update it to use the `instantsearch.js` build from the current branch.\r\n\r\nTo achieve this, this PR makes the following changes:\r\n* Remove `instantsearch.js` from dependencies\r\n* Alias `instantsearch.js` to use the build in the parent directory (using [Parcel aliases](https://parceljs.org/module_resolution.html#alias) and [TypeScript path mapping](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/module-resolution.html#path-mapping))\r\n* Update `website:build` command to build `instantsearch` before the demos",
